<p class="ql-align-justify">2020-2021年的美本申请季已经到来，准备申请秋季入学的你们准备好了吗？除了Common App 系统的文书题目，美国各大高校通常有自己的补充文书题目，目前已有30多所大学公布了补充文书题目，有些学校较往年的基础上改变了题目。比如芝加哥大学。下面我们一起来看看吧！(注：序号代表了大学排名）</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3. Yale University 耶鲁大学</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">前3题不超过125字，后面提问35字以内。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200809/eee400d860304fd8bb8272aafba30b38.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3. . Columbia University 哥伦比亚大学</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200809/72a9f3cccf0745e7b9ac7dde4ea25173.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不超过200字</p>
<p>1、List the titles of the required readings from academic courses that you enjoyed most during secondary/high school.</p>
<p>2、List the titles of the books, essays, poetry, short stories or plays you read outside of academic courses that you enjoyed most during secondary/high school.best essay writing service on www.lxws.net</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
